  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="KT339-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">varaiviṭai vēṟupaṭṭa kiḻattiyait tōḻi kaṭuñcol colli vaṟpuṟīiyatu. </p>


        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">The confidante encouraging, speaking harsh words to HER,
          who had changed [awaiting] the time of marriage. </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="KT339">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> naṟaiyakil vayaṅkiya naḷipuṉa naṟumpukai</l>
          <l> yuṟaiyaṟu maiyiṟ pōkic cāraṟ</l>
          <l> kuṟavar pākkat tiḻitaru nāṭaṉ</l>
          <l> mayaṅkumalark kōtai naṉmārpu muyaṅka</l>
          <l> liṉitumaṉ vāḻi tōḻi māyitaḻk</l>
          <l> kuvaḷai yuṇkaṇ kaluḻap</l>
          <l> pacalai yākā vūṅkalaṅ kaṭaiyē.</l>


        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l>To embrace the good chest with a garland of different blossoms</l>
          <l rend="indent">of the man from a land, where fragrant smoke from the vast fields,</l>
          <l rend="indent7">on which fragrant eagle wood has glowed up,</l>
          <l rend="indent">goes like dropless clouds </l>
          <l rend="indent">[and] comes down into the village of the hill people on the slope,</l>
          <l>[that is] sweet indeed, oh friend,</l>
          <l rend="indent2">before pallor comes, at the end of night,</l>
          <l rend="indent4">for collyrium eyes to dim, black-petalled waterlilies.</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
